---
import Download from "@icons/Download.astro";
import Person from "@icons/Person.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="max-w-7xl m-auto mt-25">
  <div class="flex items-end mt-7 gap-4">
    <Person class="size-8" />
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">
      Sobre <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 text-transparent bg-clip-text">mí</span>
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-10 mt-10">
    <img class="rounded-4xl w-52" src="/imagenes/dionisio.jpg" alt="Imagen de Dionisio Rodriguez">
    <div class="max-w-2xl pt-3">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium">Dionisio Rodriguez</h2>
      <h4 class="mt-3 mb-7 font-bold text-lg">
        <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 text-transparent bg-clip-text">Desarrollador</span>
        <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-600  text-transparent bg-clip-text">Frontend</span>
      </h4>
      <p class="text-balance">Hola, soy un desarrollador frontend apasionado por crear experiencias digitales únicas. Me encanta trabajar con tecnologías modernas y siempre estoy en busqueda de aprender y mejorar mis habilidades.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
      <button class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer px-5 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 flex items-center gap-4
      inset-ring-2 hover:scale-105 transition duration 1s ease-in-out shadow-lg">
        <Download />
        Descargar mi CV
      </button>
    </div>
</section>